                <h1>Maximizing iOS Background Modes: Boost App Efficiency</h1>
                <p>iOS Background Modes allow apps to perform specific tasks while running in the background. This enhances user experience by enabling functionalities like audio playback, location updates, and VoIP calls without interruption. Proper implementation is crucial for preserving battery life and maintaining efficiency in app performance.</p>
